original: Jahn, Erik Olof Fredrik, direktör, Göteborg, f. 16/4/05 i Västerås. G. 31 m. Maj Andersson. Barn: Mikael f. 33, Katarina 38, Cecilia 42. — Stud:-ex. 23. Anst. v. Davies & Royle Ltd i London 23-24, TExpansion Franco-Scandinave i Paris 25-26, Papierfabr. Sebnitz AG i Sebnitz i Sachsen 27-28, Wargöns Pappersbruk 29-31, Ekman & Co. A-B i Gbg 31-34, inneh. av samt verkst. dir. f. A-B Pumpindustri i Gbg sed. 35.
translated: Jahn, Erik Olof Fredrik, director, Gothenburg, born April 16th, 1905 in Västerås. Married in 1931 to Maj Andersson. Children: Mikael born in 1933, Katarina born in 1938, Cecilia born in 1942. - Graduated from high school in 1923. Employed by Davies & Royle Ltd in London from 1923-1924, TExpansion Franco-Scandinave in Paris from 1925-1926, Papierfabr. Sebnitz AG in Sebnitz in Saxony from 1927-1928, Wargön's Paper Mill from 1929-1931, Ekman & Co. AB in Gothenburg from 1931-1934, owner and managing director for AB Pump Industry in Gothenburg since 1935.
